item.title: Will Adrian Martinez Satisfy K-State Fans?
item.description: Skylar Thompson, the QB for K-State since 2017, created quite the fan base among Wildcat fans during his five seasons with the university. Thompsonâ€™s last year of eligibility with Kansas State was 2021 and Wildcat fans were anxious to find out who would be replacing him. After spending four years at the University of Nebraska-Lincoln, quarterback Adrian Martinez decided to enter the transfer portal and continue his football career at Kansas State University.

item.title: A Plain Markdown Post
item.description: This is a post written in plain Markdown (*.md) instead of R Markdown (*.Rmd). The major differences are: You cannot run any R code in a plain Markdown document, whereas in an R Markdown document, you can embed R code chunks (```{r}); A plain Markdown post is rendered through Blackfriday, and an R Markdown document is compiled by rmarkdown and Pandoc. There are many differences in syntax between Blackfriday’s Markdown and Pandoc’s Markdown.
